{
  "rationale": "To achieve systematic coverage and avoid oscillations, introduce helper states for turning maneuvers and ensure the robot only moves forward when the path is clear. When encountering obstacles, the supervisor chooses turning actions to navigate around them, avoiding repeated back-and-forth motions. The transitions guarantee reactions to all uncontrollable events in every state.",
